properties.areaDesc: South Laramie Range Foothills; South Laramie Range
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 11 at 2:28AM MST until February 12 at 6:00AM MST by NWS Cheyenne WY
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 45 mph with gusts up to 65 mph.

* WHERE...South Laramie Range and South Laramie Range Foothills.

* WHEN...From 8 PM this evening to 6 AM MST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris, damage property
and cause power outages. Travel will be difficult especially
for lightweight, high profile vehicles and campers.
properties.instruction:
People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown
around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 8 PM THIS EVENING TO 6 AM MST WEDNESDAY
